com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk

Class TGOverrideConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk.TGConfiguration
      • com.tallygo.tallygoandroid.sdk.TGOverrideConfiguration

  • public class TGOverrideConfiguration
extends TGConfiguration
    Used to provide an override configuration to an instance of a TGConfigurationOwner. This allows control over the configuration of individual instances without affecting other users of the TallyGo SDK configuration.
